  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Deaf children&apos;s access to quality education in Kilimanjaro Region</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This grant is supporting Signal and its partners in Tanzania to learn more about the situation of deaf children in the Kilimanjaro region so together they can develop stronger plans to improve their lives. This project measures how many deaf children are either attending or not attending primary schools in the Kilimanjaro region of Tanzania. It consults with parents, communities, teachers and government workers so that it can form a better understanding of the barriers that prevent deaf children from going to school, and identify future opportunities to improve the quality of life and schooling for deaf children.</narrative>
  </description>
